Comic Related Movies

300: Based on the comic book of the same name by writer Frank Miller and released by Dark Horse Comics

Watchmen: Based on the comic book of the same name by writer Alan Moore and released by DC Comics

Man of Steel: A reboot of the Superman movie franchise

Batman vs. Superman: Dawn of Justice: Sequel to the Man of Steel movie also featuring Batman.

description: Nathan Lueth is an professional Illustrator/Comic Book Artist based in Saint Paul, MN. He has illustrated several comic titles for Round Table Comics, including a graphic novel adaptation of the US Constitution, the We Are Heroes series for Stone Arch Books, and Impure Blood (impurebloodwebcomic.com) a steampunk fantasy webcomic written by his wife, Nadja Baer.
